defs.name: Config
defs.value: Config { nameservers, sortlist, debug, ndots, timeout, attempts, rotate, no_check_names, inet6, ip6_bytestring, ip6_dotint, edns0, single_request, single_request_reopen, no_tld_query, use_vc }
defs.docs:
Represent a resolver configuration, as described in `man 5 resolv.conf`.
 The options and defaults match those in the linux `man` page.

defs.name: nameservers
defs.docs: List of nameservers

defs.name: sortlist
defs.docs: List of preferred addresses

defs.name: debug
defs.docs: Enable DNS resolve debugging

defs.name: ndots
defs.docs: Number of dots in name to try absolute resolving first (default 1)

defs.name: timeout
defs.docs: Dns query timeout (default 5 [sec])

defs.name: attempts
defs.docs: Number of attempts to resolve name if server is inaccesible (default 2)

defs.name: rotate
defs.docs: Round-robin selection of servers (default false)

defs.name: no_check_names
defs.docs: Don't check names for validity (default false)

defs.name: inet6
defs.docs: Try AAAA query before A

defs.name: ip6_bytestring
defs.docs:
Use reverse lookup of ipv6 using bit-label format described instead
 of nibble format

defs.name: ip6_dotint
defs.docs:
Do ipv6 reverse lookups in ip6.int zone instead of ip6.arpa
 (default false)

defs.name: edns0
defs.docs: Enable dns extensions described in RFC 2671

defs.name: single_request
defs.docs: Don't make ipv4 and ipv6 requests simultaneously

defs.name: single_request_reopen
defs.docs: Use same socket for the A and AAAA requests

defs.name: no_tld_query
defs.docs: Don't resolve unqualified name as top level domain

defs.name: use_vc
defs.docs: Force using TCP for DNS resolution

defs.name: new
defs.docs: Create a new `Config` object with default values.

defs.name: parse
defs.docs: Parse a buffer and return the corresponding `Config` object.

defs.name: get_last_search_or_domain
defs.docs: Return the suffixes declared in the last "domain" or "search" directive.

defs.name: get_domain
defs.docs: Return the domain declared in the last "domain" directive.

defs.name: get_search
defs.docs: Return the domains declared in the last "search" directive.

defs.name: set_domain
defs.docs: Set the domain corresponding to the "domain" directive.

defs.name: set_search
defs.docs: Set the domains corresponding the "search" directive.

defs.name: glibc_normalize
defs.docs: Normalize config according to glibc rulees

defs.name: get_nameservers_or_local
defs.docs: Get nameserver or on the local machine

defs.name: get_system_domain
defs.docs: Get domain from config or fallback to the suffix of a hostname

defs.name: DomainIter
defs.docs: An iterator returned by [`Config.get_last_search_or_domain`](struct.Config.html#method.get_last_search_or_domain)
